data.title: If no job is safe from AI, what happens next? This expert weighs in | CNN
data.description: As AI rapidly advances toward human-level performance, some experts warn that no job will be safe from automation. Roman Yampolskiy, author of ‘AI: Unexplainable, Unpredictable, Uncontrollable’ joins Smerconish to discuss the future of the workforce.
data.author: TARA COUGHLIN
